column2: SELECT TOP #   G.ObjID, S.plate, S.mjd, S.fiberid, S.specObjID, G.ra, G.dec, S.z, S.zWarning,   G.u, G.Err_u, G.g, G.Err_g, G.r, G.Err_r, G.i, G.Err_i, G.z, G.Err_z,   GSL.h_alpha_reqw, GSL.h_alpha_reqw_err, GSL.h_alpha_cont,   GSL.h_beta_reqw, GSL.h_beta_reqw_err, GSL.h_beta_cont,   GSI.lick_hg_a, GSI.lick_hg_a_err, GSL.h_gamma_cont,   GSI.lick_hd_a, GSI.lick_hd_a_err, GSL.h_delta_cont,   GSI.d4#_n, GSI.d4#_n_err,   GSL.oii_#_reqw, GSL.oii_#_reqw_err, GSL.oii_#_cont,   GSL.oii_#_reqw, GSL.oii_#_reqw_err, GSL.oii_#_cont,   GSL.oiii_#_reqw, GSL.oiii_#_reqw_err, GSL.oiii_#_cont,   GSL.nii_#_reqw, GSL.nii_#_reqw_err, GSL.nii_#_cont,   GSL.sii_#_reqw, GSL.sii_#_reqw_err, GSL.sii_#_cont,   GSL.sii_#_reqw, GSL.sii_#_reqw_err, GSL.sii_#_cont into   mydb.Hd_abs7 FROM   Galaxy as G   JOIN SpecObj as S ON G.ObjID = S.BestObjId   JOIN GalSpecLine as GSL ON GSL.specobjid = G.specobjID   JOIN GalSpecIndx as GSI ON GSI.specobjid = G.specobjID WHERE    s.class = &&&    AND s.survey = &&&   AND s.programname = &&&
